@tjprescott I believe you are referencing the [OAuth](https://github.com/Azure/azure-cli-extensions/tree/master/src/storage-preview#included-features) feature that is included with the storage-preview extension, which will use the user's credentials to authenticate given the `--auth-mode` parameter. 
